---
import MarketingLayout from "@/layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
---

<MarketingLayout>
	<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="container-wide px-4 pt-16 pb-20 sm:px-6 sm:pt-24 sm:pb-28 lg:px-10 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-36">
			<div class="max-w-4xl">
				<p
					class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border bg-bg-elevated/60 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted animate-reveal"
				>
					<span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
					Private · Fast · Beautiful
				</p>
				<h1
					class="font-display text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.02em] text-balance sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl animate-reveal"
					style="animation-delay: 60ms"
				>
					A quiet place <br class="hidden sm:block" /> for the thoughts <br class="hidden sm:block" />
					<span class="italic text-accent">worth keeping.</span>
				</h1>
				<p
					class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-fg-muted sm:text-xl animate-reveal"
					style="animation-delay: 160ms"
				>
					Journal is a daily companion for writing, reflection, memory keeping, and personal
					growth. Capture today. Revisit a year. Notice who you're becoming. Your words stay
					yours — encrypted in transit, private by default, and fully on the free plan.
				</p>
				<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row animate-reveal" style="animation-delay: 240ms">
					<a
						href="/signup"
						class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-ink px-6 text-base font-medium text-paper no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-ink-soft"
					>
						Start writing — it's free
					</a>
					<a
						href="/login"
						class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-elevated px-6 text-base font-medium no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-paper-sunken"
					>
						I have an account
					</a>
				</div>
				<p
					class="mt-4 text-xs text-fg-muted animate-reveal"
					style="animation-delay: 320ms"
				>
					Or <a href="/dashboard" class="underline decoration-border underline-offset-2 hover:decoration-accent">try as a guest</a> — no signup required.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/60 bg-paper-soft/40">
		<div class="container-wide px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-16 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 stagger">
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						01 — Capture
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl tracking-tight">Write daily, friction-free.</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-fg-muted">
						A distraction-free editor with markdown, autosave, and a reading-time display. Open
						it, write, close it. Your entry is saved the moment you stop typing.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						02 — Reflect
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl tracking-tight">See your life, not just your day.</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-fg-muted">
						Calendar, timeline, year heatmap, mood trends, streaks, and "On this day" memories
						remind you who you were last year, and how far you've come.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						03 — Own
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl tracking-tight">Your words, your file.</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-fg-muted">
						Export your entire journal to Markdown, JSON, or plain text — at any time, in your
						browser. No lock-in, no data hostage.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						04 — Moods
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl tracking-tight">Track how you feel, gently.</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-fg-muted">
						Five moods, custom emojis, mood calendar, trend lines, and longest mood streak. The
						goal is awareness, not surveillance.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						05 — Goals
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl tracking-tight">Goals that move with you.</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-fg-muted">
						Daily, weekly, monthly, or yearly targets. Write 365 days. Journal your way back
						to yourself.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						06 — Install
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl tracking-tight">Works offline, anywhere.</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-fg-muted">
						Install Journal to your home screen. It works on the train, on a plane, in the
						deep of a Sunday morning. Your changes sync when you're back online.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<div class="container-wide px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-10">
			<div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
				<div>
					<p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-muted">
						For the lifelong writers
					</p>
					<h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
						Combine the best of <em class="text-accent not-italic">Day One</em>, <em
							class="text-accent not-italic">Journey</em
						>, and the apps you've outgrown.
					</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-6 text-fg-muted">
					<p>
						Ten journal types — Daily, Gratitude, Learning, Reading, Travel, Work, Fitness,
						Dream, Research, Reflection — and a fully custom type for everything else.
					</p>
					<p>
						Tags, favorites, pinned entries, location, weather, templates, split-view editor,
						fullscreen mode. Everything the well-loved journaling apps have, and nothing you
						don't need.
					</p>
					<p class="font-display text-xl italic text-fg">
						No social network. No likes. No followers. Just you and the page.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/60">
		<div class="container-wide px-4 py-16 text-center sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-10">
			<h2 class="mx-auto max-w-3xl font-display text-3xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
				Begin where you are. <br />Begin today.
			</h2>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-base text-fg-muted sm:text-lg">
				It takes about 90 seconds to make your first entry.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
				<a
					href="/signup"
					class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-ink px-7 text-base font-medium text-paper no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-ink-soft"
				>
					Start your first entry
				</a>
				<a
					href="/dashboard"
					class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-elevated px-7 text-base font-medium no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-paper-sunken"
				>
					Try as a guest
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</MarketingLayout>
